ZH: 夕阳在西边落下。
EN: The sun sets in the west.
ZH: 春天，我喜欢去西边的山上赏花。
EN: In spring, I like to go to the mountains in the west to see the flowers.
ZH: 西边的城市比东边更现代化。
EN: The city in the west is more modern than the one in the east.
ZH: 她住在那座美丽的别墅的西边。
EN: She lives to the west of that beautiful villa.
ZH: 飞机从东方飞来，然后停在西边的机场。
EN: The plane flies in from the east and lands at the airport in the west.
ZH: 西边的大海是一个度假胜地。
EN: The sea to the west is a vacation destination.
ZH: 我们从西边的山上可以看到整个城市的景色。
EN: We can see the whole city from the mountain to the west.
ZH: 这座城市的东边是一片开阔的田野。
EN: The east side of this city is a vast field.
ZH: 我向西边看了一眼，看到了一座古老的寺庙。
EN: I looked to the west and saw an ancient temple.
ZH: 在中国，西边是日落的方向。
EN: In China, the west is the direction of the sunset.
ZH: 西边的土地适合种植玉米。
EN: The land to the west is suitable for growing corn.
ZH: 小狗一溜烟跑到了西边。
EN: The puppy ran to the west in a flash.
ZH: 这片海域西边的海底富有珊瑚。
EN: The seabed to the west is rich in coral.
ZH: 他的庄园建在城市西边的山上。
EN: His estate is built on the mountain to the west of the city.
