EN: Walking to the lake at the foot of the mountain to the west, you can see the beautiful reflection.
ZH: 他在西边的海滩上度过了一个惬意的下午。
EN: He spent a pleasant afternoon on the beach in the west.
ZH: 刚刚买了房子，是西边的一套别墅。
EN: Just bought a house, it's a villa in the west.
